The Executive Governor of Kano state, Alhaji Abba Kabir Yusuf on Monday night appointedtough talking former TETFUND boss, Abdullahi Baffa Bichi, PhD as Secretary to the State Government (SSG). Similarly, the immediate past Chairman, Kano state Chapter of the People’s Democratic Party (PDP) Hon. Shehu Wada Sagagi, as Chief of Staff. In his first appointments barely six hours after he took oath of office as the executive governor of Kano state, Alhaji Abba Kabir Yusuf, announcedDr. Farouq Kurawa as his Principal Private Secretary (PPS). A statement by Sanusi Bature Dawakin that was made available to newsmen in Kano on Monday night said the governor also appointed Hon. Abdullahi Ibrahim Rogo, as his Chief Protocol, while Sanusi Bature Dawakin Tofa, was further confirmed as the Chief Press Secretary to the governor. The signed statement explained that “these appointments take effect from today, Monday 29th May, 2023. The appointees were selected based on their track records, commitment and loyalty.” In the meantime, the Executive Governor of Kano State Alhaji Abba Kabir Yusuf has approved the appointments of Chairman, Executive Secretary and members of Kano State Pilgrims Welfare Board. Those appointed are Alhaji Yusuf LawanChairman , Alhaji Laminu Rabi’u, Executive Secretary Othrs are Shiek Abbas Abubakar Daneji – Member, Shiek Shehi Shehi Maihula- MemberAmb. Munir Lawan- Member, Shiek Isma’il Mangu, Member, Hajia Aishatu Munir Matawalle- Member, Dr. Sani Ashir- Member POLL The appointees are expected to takeover the affairs of the board immediately to ensure successful 2023 Hajj operation.